Vowel Dispersion in Ictus and Stress

This is an R Markdown Notebook. When you execute code within the notebook, the results appear beneath the code.

Try executing this chunk by clicking the Run button within the chunk or by placing your cursor inside it and pressing Cmd+Shift+Enter.

library("sjPlot")
library("lme4")
library("ggplot2")
library("broom")
library("dplyr")
library("ggpattern")
spata_df <- read.csv("vowel_master.csv", header= TRUE)


spata_df$ictus <- as.factor(spata_df$ictus)
spata_df$stressed <- as.factor(spata_df$stressed)
spata_df$stressed <- recode_factor(spata_df$stressed, "0" = "unstressed","1" = "stressed")
spata_df$quantity <- as.factor(spata_df$quantity)
spata_df$song <- as.factor(spata_df$song)
spata_df$shape <- as.factor(spata_df$shape)

spata_df$word <- as.factor(spata_df$word)
spata_df
#filter out all vowel phonemes that don't occur in both stressed and unstressed positions in Estonian
space_data <- filter(spata_df, spata_df$quantity != "3" & (spata_df$segment == "a" |spata_df$segment == "aa"|spata_df$segment == "a"| spata_df$segment == "e" |spata_df$segment == "ee"| spata_df$segment == "e"  | spata_df$segment == "i" | spata_df$segment == "ii"| spata_df$segment == "i" | spata_df$segment == "o"| spata_df$segment == "oo"| spata_df$segment == "o") )
                     
#spata_df$quantity!="3" & spata_df$segment != ""
#&spata_df$segment != ""& spata_df$segment !=  ""&spata_df$segment !=  ""
#& spata_df$segment != "" &spata_df$segment != ""&spata_df$segment != ""
#& spata_df$segment != "" & spata_df$segment != "y")

(space_data)

ggplot(space_data, aes(ictus,euclid)) + 
  geom_jitter(color = "violet", alpha = 0.5) +
  facet_wrap("song") +
  labs(x = "beat position", y = "vowel dispersion") + 
  theme_classic()
ggsave("song_euc_ictus.png")
Saving 7.29 x 4.51 in image

space_data %>%
  arrange(euclid) %>%
  mutate(stressed = factor(stressed, levels = c("stressed", "unstressed")))%>%
  ggplot(aes(stressed,euclid)) + 
    geom_jitter(color = "orange", alpha = 0.5) +
    facet_wrap("song") +
    labs(x = "word stress", y = "vowel dispersion") + 
    theme_classic()
ggsave("song_euc_stress.png")
Saving 7.29 x 4.51 in image

ggplot(space_data, aes(ictus,euclid)) + 
  geom_jitter(color = "violet", alpha = 0.5) +
  facet_wrap("performer") +
  labs(x = "beat position", y = "vowel dispersion") + 
  theme_minimal()
ggsave("perf_euc_ictus.png")

space_data %>%
  arrange(euclid) %>%
  mutate(stressed = factor(stressed, levels = c("stressed", "unstressed")))%>%
  ggplot(aes(x=stressed ,y=euclid,pattern = ictus)) + 
  
  geom_boxplot_pattern()  + 
  
  #geom_jitter( alpha = 0.5) +
  theme_classic() +
  labs( x= "word stress" ,y = "euclidean distance(Hz) from center of (F1, F2) plane", pattern = "beat position", title = "spatial effects on vowels of stressed and unstressed syllables") 

ggsave('space_strictus.png')

desmd <- lmer(euclid ~ stressed + ictus + stressed*ictus + (1|syll)+ (1|performer), REML = FALSE, data = space_data )
